<h1 style="text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: xx-large;"><strong>《</strong><strong>声诗润朱弦</strong><strong>》</strong></span></h1>
<h2 style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><strong>      时间：2012年9月29日                       地点：国家大剧院音乐厅</strong></span></h2>
<h2 style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><strong>      指挥：阎伯政（国家一级指挥）       钢琴伴奏：全艳  王燕               主持：张思路</strong></span></h2>
<h2 style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><strong>      演唱：中央民族乐团民歌合唱队       演奏：中央民族乐团喜洋洋室内乐队</strong></span></h2>
<p><br /><br /></p>
 
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><br /><br /><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">一、     琴歌合唱《子夜吴歌》                                                                                    [唐]李白词 王迪定谱 </span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                       《春光好》                                                            [唐]欧阳炯词 王迪定谱 赵弟军配器</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                                 古琴演奏：邓红（管派传人）   箫演奏：马芸(文华奖获奖者)<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br /><br />二、     琴、箫合奏《梅花三弄》                                                                                      选自《琴箫合谱》</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                               古琴演奏：邓红              箫演奏：马芸<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br /><br />三、女声独唱《杏花天影》                                                                                [宋]姜夔词曲 杨荫浏译谱</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;">                              演唱：裴长佳<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;"><br /><br />四、男中音独唱《大江东去》                                                                                         [宋]苏轼词 青主曲</span></span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                              演唱：刘扬(文化部文华奖获奖者、文化部首届中国歌剧节获奖者)<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br /><br />五、女声合唱《枉凝眉》                                                                      电视剧《红楼梦》插曲 王立平曲</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                 《编花篮小景》                                                                     根据河南民歌 张以达编合唱<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br /><br />六、唢呐独奏《百鸟朝凤》                                                                                                     山东民间乐曲</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                             演奏：陈力宝<br /></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;"><br /><br /> </span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;">七、小合奏《君子兰》                                                                                                                     刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">              《渔舟凯歌》                                                                                                            刘文金编配</span></p>
