<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                           领唱：张平（国家一级演员） 张向华（文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br />九、诗乐和鸣《春江花月夜》                                                                                        [唐]张若虚诗 古曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                           琵琶演奏：蒋彦      朗诵：张思路</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br />十、男声四重唱《万叶千声》                                                                                [宋]欧阳修词  刘家昌曲</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                      《菊花台》                                                                    方文山词 周杰伦曲 王志信改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;">                           演唱：张向华   肖笑  刘松焘    赵健<br /></span><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: small;"><br /><br />十一、女高音独唱《木兰从军》                                                                                      刘麟词 王志信曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;">                           演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="a" style="padding-left: 60px;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; color: #000000; font-size: small;"><br />十二、民歌合唱《瑶山夜歌》                                                         根据民族管弦乐《瑶族舞曲》改编</span></p>
